[english]

I  have collected few computer  science problems (in  Caml Light) on a
Web page. Unfortunately, the problems are *in french*. They were given
to first degree students, in 2 hours  sessions.  Each one is available
with a solution. All the stuff  is available either by  HTTP or by FTP
at

	http://www.ens-lyon.fr/~jcfillia/tp_caml.fr.html
	ftp://ftp.ens-lyon.fr/pub/users/LIP/jcfillia/tp-info/

All comments are welcome.

